---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — robinson-cursor.com" description="Privacy policy for robinson-cursor.com.">
  <article class="privacy-page">
    <h1>privacy policy</h1>

    <section>
      <h2>controller</h2>
      <p>
        Marius Bruns<br />
        Piependamm 8<br />
        28279 Bremen, Germany<br />
        mareisen@pm.me
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>hosting</h2>
      <p>
        This website is hosted on <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Pages</a>
        (Cloudflare, Inc., 101 Townsend St, San Francisco, CA 94107, USA).
        When you visit this site, Cloudflare may process your IP address, browser type,
        operating system, referrer URL, and access time in server logs.
        This is necessary for delivering the website and constitutes a legitimate interest
        pursuant to Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR.
      </p>
      <p>
        Cloudflare is certified under the EU-U.S. Data Privacy Framework.
        For details, see
        <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's privacy policy</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>what data is collected</h2>
      <p>
        This website does <strong>not</strong> use cookies, analytics, tracking scripts,
        or any third-party services beyond Cloudflare hosting.
        No personal data is collected, stored, or processed by the website operator
        beyond what Cloudflare logs automatically (see above).
      </p>
      <p>
        No fonts, scripts, or resources are loaded from external servers.
        All assets are served from the same domain.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>external links</h2>
      <p>
        This site contains links to external websites (e.g. GitHub).
        The operator has no control over the content or privacy practices of those sites.
        Please refer to their respective privacy policies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>your rights</h2>
      <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request information about your stored personal data (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data (Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Request restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Object to processing (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority (Art. 77 GDPR)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        The competent supervisory authority is:<br />
        Die Landesbeauftragte für Datenschutz und Informationsfreiheit der Freien Hansestadt Bremen<br />
        Arndtstraße 1, 27570 Bremerhaven<br />
        <a href="https://www.datenschutz.bremen.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.datenschutz.bremen.de</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        This privacy policy may be updated to reflect changes in legal requirements
        or site functionality. The current version is always available at this URL.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    max-width: 680px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .privacy-page section {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .privacy-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .privacy-page p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .privacy-page ul {
    margin: var(--space-sm) 0 var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .privacy-page li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .privacy-page strong {
    color: var(--color-text-heading);
  }
</style>
